{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in any case, at the beginning, you know, I say, it was warm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't so bad to be in this queue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after that, when it was very cold, and we couldn't-- we couldn't stay, you know, for three hours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were trying, you know, to be, you know, against each other-- the bodies of warm body, to give little bit of warm to another body in front of us, on the other side.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you have to be five in a row.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And come this [NON-ENGLISH] with a stick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have to keep a distance from one to another person, like, at least one meter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like that-- the wind, and the cold, and the snow will come to you in all direction-- in your face, in your [? everything. ?] Imagine-- no hair; into your ears-- it was cold, cold, cold-- like that.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't imagine how much cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And still, we were enduring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't do nothing else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But people were dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Beside, you know, every week-- every week-- you know, and not every week-- every three days, coming the German there to have the selection.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The selection means taking-- for instance, they wanted to die for-- today for the-- for their crematorium, so many thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They will grab at random.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they take it from the block 20 so many-- from block 20, until they reach their number to be cremated and asphyxiated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- otherwise, you were also dying for-- from-- from diseases, which it was cholera.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was very much there-- cholera, typhus, and sort of disease of the skin.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
